# XRSound for Orbiter 2016

* Automatically adds sounds to all Orbiter vessels that define thrusters.
* Includes a default library of over 450 sounds, including all XR vessel voice callouts by actress Sally Beaumont and
  141 ATC callouts from STS-114 and STS-121 featuring CAPCOM Julie Payette.
* All sounds are fully configurable via `$ORBITER_ROOT\XRSound\XRSound.cfg`.
* Includes a simple-to-use C++ API and support for vessel class-specific configuration files to add custom sounds to
  your own Orbiter vessels.

Please refer to the XRSound User Manual installed to `$ORBITER_ROOT\Doc\XRSound User Manual.pdf` for more information.

As always, the latest version of XRSound is available at <http://www.alteaaerospace.com>.  Happy orbiting!
END_DESC
